    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies the syntax of Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) schemes for the Traversal Using Relays around NAT (TURN) protocol.  It defines two URI schemes to provision the TURN Resolution Mechanism (RFC 5928).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
